spec_data.Name: virtme
spec_data.Description:
Virtme is a set of simple tools to run a virtualized Linux kernel that
uses the host Linux distribution or a simple rootfs instead of a whole
disk image.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 08:15:07 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Virtualize the running distro or a simple rootfs
